                "invention-title": [
                    "Capacity double-layer optimization configuration method for long-short-term multi-energy cloud energy storage system containing hydrogen refueling station multi-microgrid system",
                    "一种含加氢站多微网系统的长短时多能源云储能系统容量双层优化配置方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a capacity optimization configuration method for a long-short time multi-energy cloud energy storage system of a multi-micro-grid system containing a hydrogen refueling station, and the method comprises the steps: firstly providing a multi-micro-grid system structure containing the hydrogen refueling station, and applying the multi-energy cloud energy storage system with long-short time energy storage characteristics to the multi-micro-grid system; secondly, energy storage behaviors are analyzed from the angle of a hydrogen refueling station-containing multi-microgrid system and the angle of a cloud energy storage system, and information interaction and energy charging and discharging control are carried out through a system operator; then, a multi-microgrid-operator planning model is established on the upper layer to optimize the energy storage cost of the multi-microgrid system side, a cloud energy storage-operator planning model is established on the lower layer to optimize the capacity of each energy storage device, and therefore a multi-microgrid-operator-cloud energy storage multi-body double-layer planning model is established; and finally, the overall capacity of the cloud energy storage system is optimized and configured according to the energy storage demand information transmitted by the upper layer, so that the economical efficiency of the overall system is optimal, efficient energy storage sharing oriented to the hydrogen refueling station-containing multi-microgrid system is realized, and clean low-carbon application of multi-energy interconnection is promoted."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种含加氢站多微网系统的长短时多能源云储能系统容量优化配置方法，首先提出一种含加氢站的多微网系统结构，并将具有长短时储能特性的多能源云储能系统应用于该多微网系统之中；其次分别从含加氢站多微网系统角度和云储能系统角度分析储能行为，并通过系统运营商进行二者信息交互和充放能控制；然后上层建立多微网‑运营商规划模型以优化多微网系统侧储能成本，下层建立云储能‑运营商规划模型以优化各储能设备容量，从而建立多微网‑运营商‑云储能的多主体双层规划模型；最后通过上层传递的储能需求信息进行云储能系统的整体容量优化配置从而实现整体系统经济性最优，本发明实现面向含加氢站多微网系统的高效储能共享，促进多能源互联的清洁低碳应用。"
                }
            ]
